title: 197. Q&AF: Starting From Scratch, Taking Capital Investments & Becoming Truly Undeniable
itunes:title: 197. Q&AF: Starting From Scratch, Taking Capital Investments & Becoming Truly Undeniable
description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on the path he would take in business if he had to start over from scratch, the pros & cons of taking capital investment when starting your business, and what to do if your boss doesn't or refuses to see that you're becoming undeniable.
